# Tax and Compliance Standards

## Tax Calculation
- Implement Stripe Tax for automatic tax calculation
- Apply proper tax codes to products and services
- Create consistent tax display in checkout flows
- Document tax calculation logic and rules
- Implement proper testing for various tax scenarios

## Tax-Exempt Customers
- Create standardized tax exemption workflow
- Implement proper validation for exemption documentation
- Apply consistent storage of exemption certificates
- Document exemption renewal processes
- Create proper audit trail for exemption status changes

## Compliance Documentation
- Implement required legal documentation in checkout flows
- Apply consistent Terms of Service acceptance
- Create proper records of customer agreements
- Document compliance requirements by jurisdiction
- Implement privacy policy notifications

## Reporting and Remittance
- Create standardized tax reporting capabilities
- Implement proper record-keeping for tax obligations
- Apply consistent formatting for tax documentation
- Document tax filing requirements and deadlines
- Create export capabilities for tax reporting

